PushWard server URL:
: <input type="text" name="PUSHWARD_URL" maxlength="200" value="<?= pw_val($cfg,'PUSHWARD_URL','https://api.pushward.app') ?>">

PushWard API key:
: <input type="password" id="pushward_api_key" name="PUSHWARD_API_KEY" maxlength="200" value="" placeholder="<?= $configured ? 'leave blank to keep current key' : 'hlk_...' ?>">

Server display name:
: <input type="text" name="PUSHWARD_SERVER_NAME" maxlength="100" value="<?= pw_val($cfg,'PUSHWARD_SERVER_NAME','Unraid') ?>">

Live Activities:
: <select name="PUSHWARD_ACTIVITIES_ENABLED"><?= pw_yesno($cfg,'PUSHWARD_ACTIVITIES_ENABLED','true') ?></select>

Track parity check / rebuild:
: <select name="PUSHWARD_TRACK_PARITY"><?= pw_yesno($cfg,'PUSHWARD_TRACK_PARITY','true') ?></select>

Track appdata backup:
: <select name="PUSHWARD_TRACK_BACKUP"><?= pw_yesno($cfg,'PUSHWARD_TRACK_BACKUP','true') ?></select>

Track mover:
: <select name="PUSHWARD_TRACK_MOVER"><?= pw_yesno($cfg,'PUSHWARD_TRACK_MOVER','true') ?></select>

Poll interval (seconds):
: <input type="number" name="PUSHWARD_POLL_INTERVAL" min="5" max="300" value="<?= pw_val($cfg,'PUSHWARD_POLL_INTERVAL','15') ?>">

Activity priority (0-10):
: <input type="number" name="PUSHWARD_ACTIVITY_PRIORITY" min="0" max="10" value="<?= pw_val($cfg,'PUSHWARD_ACTIVITY_PRIORITY','5') ?>">

&nbsp;
: <input type="submit" name="apply" value="Apply"> <input type="button" value="Done" onclick="done()">

</form>

<script>
// Never render the stored API key into the page (View-Source / DOM / form-cache
// would leak it). The field ships empty; if left blank on Apply, drop its name
// so it isn't POSTed and update.php preserves the existing key (it merges the
// POST over the on-disk cfg). A typed value overwrites as normal.
function pwKeepKey() {
  var k = document.getElementById('pushward_api_key');
  if (k && k.value === '') k.removeAttribute('name');
  return true;
}
</script>

<form markdown="1" name="pushward_unraid_test" method="POST" action="/update.php" target="progressFrame">
<input type="hidden" name="#command" value="/usr/local/emhttp/plugins/<?= $plugin ?>/test.sh">
